---
import Page from '@/layouts/Page.astro';
---

<Page
  title="Privacy<br><em>policy</em>"
  label="Legal"
  description="How Vox Essay Mosaic collects, uses, and protects your personal information."
  currentPage="privacy"
>
  <section class="content-section">
    <div class="content-inner">
      <p class="legal-effective">Effective Date: February 1, 2026</p>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2 class="legal-section-title">Introduction</h2>
        <p>
          Luminous Estates LLC ("we," "us," or "Vox Mosaic") operates the website
          voxmosaic.com. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose,
          and safeguard your information when you visit our website or submit content
          to our publication.
        </p>
        <p>
          By using our website, you agree to the collection and use of information
          in accordance with this policy. If you do not agree, please do not use our site.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2 class="legal-section-title">Information We Collect</h2>

        <h3 class="legal-subsection">Information You Provide</h3>
        <p>We collect information you voluntarily provide when you:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Subscribe to our email list:</strong> Email address
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Submit an essay:</strong> Name, email address, essay content,
            biographical information, headshot photo, website/social media links,
            and publication history
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Contact us:</strong> Name, email address, and message content
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="legal-subsection">Information Collected Automatically</h3>
        <p>When you visit our website, we may automatically collect:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Analytics data:</strong> Page views, scroll depth, referral source,
            and general geographic region. We use Umami Analytics, a privacy-focused
            service that does not use cookies or collect personal identifiers.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Server logs:</strong> Our hosting provider (Vercel) may collect
            IP addresses and browser information for security and performance purposes.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2 class="legal-section-title">How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Send you updates about Vox Mosaic, including edition launches and news</li>
          <li>Review and respond to essay submissions</li>
          <li>Create and publish author profiles for accepted contributors</li>
          <li>Respond to your inquiries and communications</li>
          <li>Improve our website and understand how visitors use it</li>
          <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2 class="legal-section-title">Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>We use the following third-party services that may process your data:</p>

        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Tally (tally.so):</strong> Submission form hosting. When you submit
            an essay, your information is processed through Tally's servers.
            <a href="https://tally.so/help/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">View Tally's Privacy Policy</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Email Service Provider:</strong> We use an email service to manage
            our mailing list. Your email address is stored with our provider to send
            you updates you've requested.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Umami Analytics:</strong> Privacy-focused analytics that does not
            use cookies or collect personally identifiable information.
            <a href="https://umami.is/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">View Umami's Privacy Policy</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Vercel:</strong> Website hosting and delivery.
            <a href="https://vercel.com/legal/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">View Vercel's Privacy Policy</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2 class="legal-section-title">Data Retention</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Email subscribers:</strong> We retain your email address until you
            unsubscribe or request deletion.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Submissions:</strong> We retain submission data for the duration
            of our review process. Accepted contributors' information is retained as
            long as their work is published. Declined submissions are deleted within
            90 days of notification.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Published author profiles:</strong> Retained for as long as the
            edition remains published, or until the contributor requests removal per
            the Contributor Agreement.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2 class="legal-section-title">Your Rights</h2>

        <h3 class="legal-subsection">All Users</h3>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Unsubscribe from our email list at any time using the link in any email</li>
          <li>Request access to the personal information we hold about you</li>
          <li>Request correction of inaccurate information</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your personal information</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="legal-subsection">California Residents (CCPA)</h3>
        <p>If you are a California resident, you have additional rights under the California Consumer Privacy Act:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>The right to know what personal information we collect, use, and disclose</li>
          <li>The right to request deletion of your personal information</li>
          <li>The right to non-discrimination for exercising your privacy rights</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          We do not sell your personal information. To exercise any of these rights,
          contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@voxmosaic.com">privacy@voxmosaic.com</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2 class="legal-section-title">Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          Our website does not use cookies for tracking or analytics. Umami Analytics
          is cookie-free by design. Some third-party embeds (such as our submission form)
          may use their own cookies as described in their respective privacy policies.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2 class="legal-section-title">Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          Our website is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect
          personal information from children under 13. If you believe we have collected
          information from a child under 13, please contact us immediately.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2 class="legal-section-title">Security</h2>
        <p>
          We implement reasonable security measures to protect your personal information.
          However, no method of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure. While we
          strive to protect your information, we cannot guarantee absolute security.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2 class="legal-section-title">Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of
          any changes by posting the new policy on this page and updating the effective
          date. Significant changes will be communicated via email to subscribers.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2 class="legal-section-title">Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, contact us at:</p>
        <p>
          <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:privacy@voxmosaic.com">privacy@voxmosaic.com</a><br>
          <strong>General inquiries:</strong> <a href="mailto:hello@voxmosaic.com">hello@voxmosaic.com</a>
        </p>
        <p class="legal-entity">
          Luminous Estates LLC<br>
          Operating as Vox Essay Mosaic
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="page-cta">
    <div class="page-cta-inner">
      <h2 class="page-cta-title">Questions?</h2>
      <p class="page-cta-text">
        We're committed to transparency. Reach out anytime.
      </p>
      <div class="page-cta-buttons">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Contact Us</a>
        <a href="/terms" class="btn-secondary">Terms of Service</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Page>

<style>
  .legal-effective {
    color: var(--gray-500);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .legal-section {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
  }

  .legal-section:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .legal-section-title {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    color: var(--gray-900);
  }

  .legal-subsection {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-top: var(--space-6);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
    color: var(--gray-800);
  }

  .legal-section p {
    color: var(--gray-700);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .legal-section ul {
    color: var(--gray-700);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    padding-left: var(--space-6);
  }

  .legal-section li {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .legal-section a {
    color: var(--gray-900);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .legal-section a:hover {
    color: var(--gray-600);
  }

  .legal-entity {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--gray-500);
    margin-top: var(--space-4);
  }
</style>
